WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.870
Hey, good morning family. I'm excited to

00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:03.790
be with you all again today. I have some

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:05.630
things I want to talk to you about,

00:00:05.640 --> 00:00:07.510
but first of all, I just want to say

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:09.750
thank you for all the likes, the

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:12.870
subscribes, and the comments. It's a true

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:15.270
blessing to us, and we just want to say

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:18.070
thank you for supporting this YouTube

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:20.109
channel as you have. God bless you

00:00:20.119 --> 00:00:22.509
all. I pray for you daily that the Lord

00:00:22.519 --> 00:00:25.589
increases you in every area of your

00:00:25.589 --> 00:00:25.599
life—physically,

00:00:25.599 --> 00:00:27.589
spiritually, financially,

00:00:27.599 --> 00:00:29.990
emotionally, everything—that the Lord

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.109
will give you abundant overflow in your

00:00:32.119 --> 00:00:34.510
homes. I just want to say

00:00:34.520 --> 00:00:35.990
thank you from the bottom of

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.069
our hearts for supporting this YouTube

00:00:38.079 --> 00:00:39.910
channel, and I appreciate your prayers

00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:41.709
for my family. I appreciate all

00:00:41.709 --> 00:00:41.719
your

00:00:41.719 --> 00:00:44.750
prayers. I'm

00:00:44.760 --> 00:00:46.270
going to do a video that I've already

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:49.069
done before, but I felt because of the

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:51.350
time that's passed since I made the

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:54.229
video that I could do it better.

00:00:54.229 --> 00:00:54.239
I

00:00:54.239 --> 00:00:56.189
listened

00:00:56.199 --> 00:00:58.189
back to it and I thought, 'I think I can

00:00:58.199 --> 00:01:00.470
do better at that.'So, let's give it a

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:04.469
shot. I've told you before

00:01:04.469 --> 00:01:04.479
how

00:01:04.479 --> 00:01:07.190
the Lord took me out of my

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:11.270
body and I shot up into outer space.

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:14.510
I could see the Lord,

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:19.270
though

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:23.469
from His midway up, I

00:01:23.479 --> 00:01:25.870
could not see anything during the

00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:28.870
whole visitation. I don't know if

00:01:28.880 --> 00:01:31.550
it was God the Father or Jesus, but I'm

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:32.670
going to tell

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:36.749
you, we were in outer space and I

00:01:36.759 --> 00:01:41.149
could see the planets. It was like

00:01:41.159 --> 00:01:42.789
everything was shrunk down. I know

00:01:42.799 --> 00:01:45.510
they're millions of miles apart,

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:47.230
but everything in the solar system

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:50.950
seemed so small to us. We were

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:54.190
looking at it like

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:56.870
the planets were right there. I

00:01:56.880 --> 00:02:00.510
could see Saturn,

00:02:00.520 --> 00:02:03.550
Jupiter, and Mars. I could see it

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:06.310
all, but we were standing right next to

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:10.350
the Sun the whole time. The Sun was

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:13.150
massive, and it was over to

00:02:13.160 --> 00:02:15.869
my right. The Lord was also to

00:02:15.879 --> 00:02:18.550
the right, and I was looking out at

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:22.390
the Sun when He spoke to me. He said,

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:25.750
'Brandon, how long does it take for the

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:30.190
Sun's light to get to the

00:02:30.190 --> 00:02:30.200
Earth?'I

00:02:30.200 --> 00:02:32.350
knew the answer. I said, 'It takes like

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:35.229
eight minutes and 20 some seconds.'Right

00:02:35.229 --> 00:02:35.239
then,

00:02:35.239 --> 00:02:38.710
I knew the answer,

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:40.670
but now I've probably butchered

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:43.430
it.

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:46.030
I told the Lord

00:02:46.030 --> 00:02:46.040
that

00:02:46.040 --> 00:02:49.830
at 186,000

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:54.589
miles per second, the light travels

00:02:54.599 --> 00:02:57.550
from the Sun and takes

00:02:57.560 --> 00:03:00.509
8 minutes and 27 seconds to get

00:03:00.509 --> 00:03:00.519
to the Earth.

00:03:00.519 --> 00:03:03.910
He asked me, 'Brandon,

00:03:03.920 --> 00:03:06.670
what is faster than the speed of

00:03:06.670 --> 00:03:06.680
light?'I

00:03:06.680 --> 00:03:11.229
said, 'I don't know,

00:03:11.229 --> 00:03:11.239
Lord.'He

00:03:11.239 --> 00:03:13.710
said, 'The speed of

00:03:13.710 --> 00:03:13.720
thought.'He

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:17.509
said, 'Brandon, whenever you

00:03:17.519 --> 00:03:19.910
die and you come to be with Me, you will

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:22.589
travel at the speed of thought, not at

00:03:22.599 --> 00:03:26.149
the speed of light.'The speed of thought

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:29.070
is actually way faster than

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:30.710
the speed of light because you

00:03:30.710 --> 00:03:30.720
are

00:03:30.720 --> 00:03:32.750
there

00:03:32.750 --> 00:03:32.760
instantly

00:03:32.760 --> 00:03:34.750
instead of

00:03:34.760 --> 00:03:37.429
traveling at

00:03:37.439 --> 00:03:40.550
186,000 miles per second. He

00:03:40.550 --> 00:03:40.560
was

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:43.830
telling me all this, and then

00:03:43.830 --> 00:03:43.840
He talked

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:45.789
to

00:03:45.799 --> 00:03:50.910
me about how far the nearest star is,

00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:51.710
which

00:03:51.720 --> 00:03:54.949
is light-years away.

00:03:54.959 --> 00:03:56.949
I don't remember exactly how far it was, but

00:03:56.959 --> 00:04:00.630
He told me it would take thousands of

00:04:00.630 --> 00:04:00.640
years to get there even

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:04.429
at 186,000

00:04:04.429 --> 00:04:04.439
miles

00:04:04.439 --> 00:04:07.270
per second.

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:12.710
Then He said, 'I

00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:14.910
want to take you and show you

00:04:14.910 --> 00:04:14.920
something.'All

00:04:14.920 --> 00:04:17.349
of a

00:04:17.359 --> 00:04:19.710
sudden, we were

00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:22.550
instantaneously there. This is where

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:24.469
it gets

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:27.710
good. What I could

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:30.510
see before me when we went into

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:35.830
this room was a massive white room.

00:04:35.840 --> 00:04:38.510
There was no beginning and

00:04:38.520 --> 00:04:41.310
no end to this

00:04:41.320 --> 00:04:43.749
room.

00:04:43.749 --> 00:04:43.759
The

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:47.270
light

00:04:47.280 --> 00:04:50.189
in the room

00:04:50.199 --> 00:04:52.469
was so piercing,

00:04:52.479 --> 00:04:54.990
but there was no

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:57.150
ceiling, no floor,

00:04:57.160 --> 00:04:59.469
nothing. It was like a dimension

00:04:59.479 --> 00:05:02.070
in

00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:06.990
itself. There before me was the

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:11.029
universe. This is heavy, but I'm

00:05:11.039 --> 00:05:14.870
telling you all it's fact. The

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:18.670
universe was in its own dimension. He

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:23.309
created a room for the

00:05:23.319 --> 00:05:27.309
universe; all the galaxies

00:05:27.309 --> 00:05:27.319
were

00:05:27.319 --> 00:05:31.110
inside of another

00:05:31.120 --> 00:05:33.189
dimension that was

00:05:33.199 --> 00:05:37.189
endless. Before me,

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:41.749
the universe was moving at the speed of

00:05:41.759 --> 00:05:44.230
light, being

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:48.830
created. I could see inside of this

00:05:48.840 --> 00:05:51.670
massive area; it looked like cauliflower

00:05:51.670 --> 00:05:51.680
clouds—like

00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:56.150
thunderclouds

00:05:56.160 --> 00:06:00.629
moving very

00:06:00.629 --> 00:06:00.639
slowly—but

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:03.749
it was forming

00:06:03.749 --> 00:06:03.759
right

00:06:03.759 --> 00:06:08.189
in front of my face. Stars were forming

00:06:08.199 --> 00:06:11.870
inside of this

00:06:11.880 --> 00:06:16.790
dimension, shrunk down. Though moving at

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:21.589
186,000 miles per second, it

00:06:21.589 --> 00:06:21.599
looked

00:06:21.599 --> 00:06:24.830
slow because He

00:06:24.840 --> 00:06:26.110
controls

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:29.950
time. He is in control of all

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:33.629
time; time does not exist around Him.

00:06:33.639 --> 00:06:37.710
At 186,000 miles per second, creating right

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:42.909
before my eyes, it was moving so

00:06:42.909 --> 00:06:42.919
slowly.

00:06:42.919 --> 00:06:47.469
I could

00:06:47.479 --> 00:06:50.150
see how big it was since the beginning when

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:52.550
He spoke it into existence, 'Let there be

00:06:52.550 --> 00:06:52.560
light.'All

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:54.430
the things He

00:06:54.440 --> 00:06:58.150
said in Genesis

00:06:58.150 --> 00:06:58.160
were

00:06:58.160 --> 00:07:01.909
moving. It was the size

00:07:01.919 --> 00:07:07.350
of a Volkswagen

00:07:07.350 --> 00:07:07.360
Beetle—I

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.710
don't know why, but that's the way it

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:11.909
stood out to me. It was that shape and it

00:07:11.919 --> 00:07:14.589
was moving in all

00:07:14.599 --> 00:07:19.070
directions—downward,

00:07:19.080 --> 00:07:24.189
upward, left, right, north,

00:07:24.199 --> 00:07:28.270
south, east, west—all at the same time,

00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:31.189
creating from the center. It was like a

00:07:31.199 --> 00:07:34.550
thunderstorm,

00:07:38.520 --> 00:07:41.430
moving

00:07:41.430 --> 00:07:41.440
slowly

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:44.469
like

00:07:44.479 --> 00:07:46.790
thunderclouds, all being formed and

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:49.629
created inside of this

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:52.510
room. Stars were moving and being

00:07:52.520 --> 00:07:55.670
created from every direction.

00:07:57.720 --> 00:08:00.230
It was all moving

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:05.309
equally.

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:12.790
He spoke to me and said,

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:15.189
'Brandon, you know in My Word

00:08:15.199 --> 00:08:18.029
where it says I can measure the

00:08:18.029 --> 00:08:18.039
span

00:08:18.039 --> 00:08:21.629
of the universe in My

00:08:21.629 --> 00:08:21.639
hand?'He

00:08:21.639 --> 00:08:23.029
said, 'I'm going to show you how I do

00:08:23.029 --> 00:08:23.039
it.'He

00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:28.309
took that universe

00:08:28.319 --> 00:08:30.950
and shrunk

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:34.589
it down right before my eyes. He said,

00:08:34.599 --> 00:08:38.990
'I create and I am able to manipulate it.'It

00:08:38.990 --> 00:08:39.000
was

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:42.509
like clay before

00:08:42.519 --> 00:08:46.070
Him. He said, 'Brandon, it is in a

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:49.230
dimension in itself,'and He could stretch

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:53.030
it out or shrink it.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:13.230
He put it in His

00:09:13.240 --> 00:09:16.750
hand, and He had the whole universe—billions

00:09:16.750 --> 00:09:16.760
and

00:09:16.760 --> 00:09:20.190
billions

00:09:28.630 --> 00:09:28.640
of

00:09:36.720 --> 00:09:38.030
galaxies—shrunk

00:09:46.360 --> 00:09:51.190
down in

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.949
this dimension. He said, 'Look, I can

00:09:52.959 --> 00:09:55.910
step into it.'He stretched it out and

00:09:55.920 --> 00:09:58.310
said, 'I can step into it or I can shrink

00:09:58.320 --> 00:10:01.430
it down, but Brandon, I measure

00:10:01.430 --> 00:10:01.440
it

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:04.350
all in My hand.'He put it in

00:10:04.360 --> 00:10:05.670
His hand—it was stretched out and he

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:07.630
showed it to me like

00:10:07.630 --> 00:10:07.640
a

00:10:07.640 --> 00:10:09.829
cube—and

00:10:09.839 --> 00:10:12.030
it was still

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:15.590
growing. It never stopped;

00:10:17.560 --> 00:10:20.190
stars were still forming in

00:10:20.200 --> 00:10:22.870
His hand as He was holding

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:25.430
it.

00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:27.310
No matter

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:28.829
how He

00:10:28.829 --> 00:10:28.839
stretched

00:10:28.839 --> 00:10:31.990
it or shrank it,

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:33.990
it was still being created.

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:57.910
I just stood there and watched.

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:04.110
I know I wasn't in my body; this

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:06.670
was more than just a dream. This happened

00:11:06.680 --> 00:11:09.790
to me over 20 years ago and I've

00:11:09.800 --> 00:11:12.550
never forgotten

00:11:12.550 --> 00:11:12.560
it. I

00:11:12.560 --> 00:11:15.629
remember every detail like it was

00:11:15.639 --> 00:11:18.629
yesterday,

00:11:18.639 --> 00:11:21.829
other than the numbers.

00:11:21.839 --> 00:11:23.310
I've told you

00:11:23.310 --> 00:11:23.320
I've

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:27.150
overcome my learning

00:11:27.160 --> 00:11:30.750
disabilities. He

00:11:30.750 --> 00:11:30.760
took

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:32.590
me then and said, 'I want to

00:11:32.600 --> 00:11:34.910
show you something

00:11:34.910 --> 00:11:34.920
else,'and

00:11:34.920 --> 00:11:38.269
He showed me

00:11:38.279 --> 00:11:42.949
Heaven. Heaven was a massive

00:11:42.959 --> 00:11:47.590
planet, about the size of three

00:11:47.600 --> 00:11:52.269
Jupiters. Heaven is a

00:11:52.279 --> 00:11:55.670
massive planet, like a dimension in

00:11:55.680 --> 00:11:59.990
itself. I could see the gold; it was

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:03.870
pure light. It was beyond

00:12:03.880 --> 00:12:05.910
comprehension; I cannot give

00:12:05.910 --> 00:12:05.920
it adequate justice

00:12:05.920 --> 00:12:09.430
with words.

00:12:12.040 --> 00:12:14.990
It

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:19.389
was inside its own

00:12:19.399 --> 00:12:21.389
dimension.

00:12:21.399 --> 00:12:25.030
The universe

00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:28.590
was on the edge

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:30.310
of Heaven.

00:12:30.310 --> 00:12:30.320
We

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:32.509
were standing out

00:12:32.509 --> 00:12:32.519
there

00:12:32.519 --> 00:12:35.990
again, and I was looking at all the walls. There

00:12:35.990 --> 00:12:36.000
are

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:38.550
massive walls all

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:41.269
around Heaven, and I

00:12:47.959 --> 00:12:49.430
could see buildings—all kinds of houses and buildings. It's like a

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:52.350
major city, but beautiful

00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:56.750
beyond words. I could see the

00:12:56.760 --> 00:13:00.069
walls formed with gold and

00:13:00.079 --> 00:13:02.670
all kinds of beautiful stones.

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:06.350
Then all

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:07.550
of a

00:13:07.560 --> 00:13:10.990
sudden I looked up, and

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:14.590
the sky above me was filled

00:13:14.590 --> 00:13:14.600
with

00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:18.710
beautiful pinks, purples, and whites,

00:13:18.720 --> 00:13:22.550
swirled like a paisley print.

00:13:39.839 --> 00:13:42.910
He said, 'Brandon, this is My

00:13:42.920 --> 00:13:47.189
portion; I set this aside for Myself,

00:13:47.199 --> 00:13:51.189
Heaven. But son, I'm

00:13:51.189 --> 00:13:51.199
giving

00:13:51.199 --> 00:13:54.670
you the universe. All the galaxies are

00:13:54.680 --> 00:13:59.110
going to be yours.'He said that is the portion He is

00:13:59.110 --> 00:13:59.120
giving to His

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:02.790
kids, the

00:14:02.790 --> 00:14:02.800
born-again

00:14:02.800 --> 00:14:06.430
believers.

00:14:06.440 --> 00:14:10.389
When

00:14:29.399 --> 00:14:31.990
you come home to be with Me after

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:35.110
the thousand-year reign, you will

00:14:35.120 --> 00:14:39.110
spend eternity traveling at the speed of

00:14:39.120 --> 00:14:42.470
thought throughout all the galaxies

00:14:42.470 --> 00:14:42.480
and

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:45.670
universes, going

00:14:45.680 --> 00:14:48.269
from one to another. There are planets

00:14:48.269 --> 00:14:48.279
and

00:14:48.279 --> 00:14:51.150
stars being made, and

00:14:51.160 --> 00:14:53.790
you will rule and reign forever

00:14:53.800 --> 00:14:58.230
and ever with Me over eternity

00:14:58.240 --> 00:14:59.949
in those

00:14:59.959 --> 00:15:02.189
places. Why people say, 'Why would I

00:15:02.199 --> 00:15:04.030
want my own galaxy?'I don't know. We have

00:15:04.040 --> 00:15:06.350
a mansion in Heaven,

00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:08.110
but I'm

00:15:08.120 --> 00:15:10.069
trying to tell you what

00:15:10.069 --> 00:15:10.079
I saw.

00:15:10.079 --> 00:15:13.590
Then He said to me,

00:15:13.600 --> 00:15:15.310
'Do you see all that?'And I could

00:15:15.320 --> 00:15:17.230
see the stars being

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:20.990
formed before me.

00:15:23.959 --> 00:15:27.230
That dimension

00:15:27.240 --> 00:15:29.710
was still being spread out, but He had

00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:31.910
opened it up and we were inside of it

00:15:31.920 --> 00:15:34.509
now. Heaven was on the edge of it, and

00:15:34.519 --> 00:15:38.189
the universe and all the galaxies

00:15:38.199 --> 00:15:43.110
were on this side.

00:15:43.120 --> 00:15:45.710
He told me, 'You

00:15:45.720 --> 00:15:47.870
will rule and reign with Me forever and

00:15:47.870 --> 00:15:47.880
ever.'You're

00:15:47.880 --> 00:15:49.990
never going to get

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:51.790
bored. You'll travel at the speed of

00:15:51.800 --> 00:15:55.069
thought to all

00:15:55.079 --> 00:15:57.309
your brothers and sisters; the whole body

00:15:57.319 --> 00:15:59.829
of Christ is going to be ruling

00:15:59.829 --> 00:15:59.839
and

00:15:59.839 --> 00:16:03.670
reigning. He's creating a new Heaven and a new Earth.

