It's time to believe God for the

00:19:43.960 --> 00:19:46.710
impossible today.

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:49.470
He's no

00:19:49.470 --> 00:19:49.480
respecter

00:19:49.480 --> 00:19:52.149
