00:19:52.149 --> 00:19:52.159
did

00:19:52.159 --> 00:19:55.110
for one, He'll do for another. God loves

00:19:55.120 --> 00:19:58.350
you and He has an amazing plan. Beloved, I

00:19:58.360 --> 00:20:00.029
