00:20:12.640 --> 00:20:14.710
We are the salt of

00:20:14.720 --> 00:20:16.990
the earth,

00:20:18.990 --> 00:20:19.000
ministering

00:20:21.799 --> 00:20:23.430
to our

00:20:23.440 --> 00:20:26.310
neighbors and telling them that Jesus loves

00:20:26.320 --> 00:20:29.190
