00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.909
coming soon, folks. I hope

00:20:31.919 --> 00:20:33.909
you're ready. I hope your heart

00:20:33.909 --> 00:20:33.919
is

00:20:33.919 --> 00:20:36.430
prepared.

