00:20:44.880 --> 00:20:47.990
coming back for

00:20:47.990 --> 00:20:48.000
you

00:20:48.000 --> 00:20:50.470
and

00:20:50.470 --> 00:20:50.480
me

00:20:50.480 --> 00:20:52.990
and those who believe and

00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:54.830
are

00:20:54.840 --> 00:20:57.470
seeking Him daily.

00:20:59.360 --> 00:21:01.470
Let me pray for you.

00:21:01.480 --> 00:21:05.390
Father, I thank You for

00:21:05.390 --> 00:21:05.400
'big.'I

00:21:05.400 --> 00:21:09.350
thank You, God, for 'huge.'I thank You

00:21:09.360 --> 00:21:10.190
for

00:21:10.190 --> 00:21:10.200
'ginormous'—that

00:21:10.200 --> 00:21:13.549
You are an awesome God

00:21:13.559 --> 00:21:16.590
