00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:31.950
have eternity;

00:21:31.960 --> 00:21:34.390
time is endless with

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:37.909
You. You have

00:21:37.919 --> 00:21:40.149
everything in the

00:21:40.159 --> 00:21:43.470
